race.description: Unox Casa Lawson Poole Plate Handicap
race.comment: Sticking with SWEETHEARTED (8) who gets to 1200m third up. Both runs back over 1100m have been good, not beaten far on either occasion and getting home well in tough conditions at Flemington when the race was won up on speed. He sets up well here and should prove very hard to hold out. STOLI BOLLI (3) has been costly for punters this time in, again turned over as favourite last time in the same Flemington lead up. He's still racing well and only needs to hold that form to be going close again. MYTEMPTATION (1) is knocking on the door, trying hard in the Ararat Bowl over 1300m last time. He'll cross over from out wide and take catching. YALDI (5) has been right there in two runs back, fourth in the Flemington race with every hope. Can figure. JASMIN ROUGE (7) was awful first up but has ability.
